00:09:08.147 --> 00:09:09.648
It's a little stomachache.

00:09:09.648 --> 00:09:11.050
I went to the doctor before
I left for Australia.

00:09:11.050 --> 00:09:12.084
He said it was gas.

00:09:12.084 --> 00:09:13.151
That's not good doctoring

00:09:13.151 --> 00:09:15.254
